{
  "texts": [
    "Five algorithms were compared in the constructed models: SoftMax SVM, SVM, Perceptron, EvoSVM, and Naïve Bayes.",
    "The researchers reported that SoftMax SVM outperformed the other algorithms across four public datasets.",
    "In addressing the research question concerning enhancing precision while maintaining high recall rates, they explored various re-sampling techniques such as SMOTE, under-sampling, and a combination of SMOTE + under-sampling.",
    "Results derived from using SMOTE + under-sampling demonstrated the highest scores for F1, precision, recall, and WSS@95 when employing a 5 × 2 cross- validation technique.",
    "Similarly, investigations by Almeida et al. (2016) delved into the potential of various re-sampling techniques, feature extraction methods, and feature selection techniques to aid in automating the screening stage."
  ]
}